Quasar:





Quasar watched Omnious' attack, and lept off of the table. In the mid 
of her leap, wings made of energon spread out from under her armor 
and caught her decent. She landed a little unsteadily, with a stunned 
look in her optics. She looked over her shoulder. Wings. The sons of 
maintenance bots built wings on her. 

She stared straight at Omnious in bane. "Slag you!"
